## Accessibility

### Focus Indicators

Always include visible focus indicators:

```typescript
focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-forvis-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2
```

### Color Contrast

Maintain WCAG AA compliance:
- Text on white: Use gray-700 or darker
- Text on blue-500: Use white
- Links: Use blue-500 with underline for clarity

### Screen Reader Support

```typescript
// Hidden visually, available to screen readers
className="sr-only"

// ARIA labels for icons
<button aria-label="Close modal">
  <XIcon className="h-5 w-5" />
</button>
```

