❌ Don't use arbitrary values unless absolutely necessary
❌ Don't introduce new color schemes
❌ Avoid default Tailwind shadows (use corporate shadows)
❌ Don't use bold text everywhere (reserve for emphasis)
❌ Avoid inconsistent spacing
❌ Don't mix px values with Tailwind classes
❌ Avoid excessive animations
